{"tid":1104801,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"玫瑰崗學校劃面事件 反映晒近年社會上嘅所有好壞人","createTime":"2019-04-13T11:32:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T11:57:22.000Z","uid":105472,"like":75,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fd0c092b84d82bb2a45472a01f9328ab89f4c3f7","tid":1104801,"uid":105472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T11:32:36.000Z","msg":"一號壞人：蝻<br />\n反映少數族裔係社會嘅縮影已經作惡多端<br />\n細個拎刀（筆） 大個拎槍棍劈劈友<br />\n<br />\n二號壞人：警<br />\n家長不在場情況下氹未成年小朋友簽和解書<br />\n為咗少啲野做 迫受害人息事寧人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1VXudcH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1VXudcH.png&h=450de3d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三號壞人：校方（教蓄）<br />\n為保校譽 力圖大事化小  掩飾傷人事件的嚴重性<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VFbbrxO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVFbbrxO.png&h=6f294bdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一號好人：醫護<br />\n阻警迫受害者簽和解書 救助傷者 誠實按醫療專業講出專業意見<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6d3ATc1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6d3ATc1.png&h=5d7ae967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n二號好人：老母<br />\n趕返黎探仔<br />\n<br />\n你信醫護 定係 校方？<br />\n<br />\n醫護：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n校方：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f88b44e8415b0773e713f14b62d8810c84e866","tid":1104801,"uid":4563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T11:38:51.000Z","msg":"黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />yijin jai 食屎啦"},{"pid":"db238b81d0bbcc1f60436daa26c7497126c7638b","tid":1104801,"uid":4563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20f88b44e8415b0773e713f14b62d8810c84e866","tid":1104801,"uid":4563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T11:38:51.000Z","msg":"黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />yijin jai 食屎啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T11:39:45.000Z","msg":"咁大件事迫